*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&      Form  ZF_SCREEN_VALIDATIONS
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
* Screen validation when partner is entered; other fields chould be blank
*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM zf_screen_validations .

* Partner Numbers or Other Criteria are needed
*  IF s_patnr  IS INITIAL AND
*     p_role   IS INITIAL AND
*     s_eccorg[] IS INITIAL AND
*     p_custcl IS INITIAL AND
*     p_sort1  IS INITIAL AND
*     p_indust IS INITIAL.
*
*    MESSAGE text-010 TYPE 'E'.
*
*  ENDIF.

* Either Partner Numbers or Other Criteria are needed BUT NOT both
*  IF s_patnr  IS NOT INITIAL AND
*   ( p_role   IS NOT INITIAL OR
*     s_eccorg[] IS NOT INITIAL OR
*     p_custcl IS NOT INITIAL OR
*     p_sort1  IS NOT INITIAL OR
*     p_indust IS NOT INITIAL ).
*
*    MESSAGE text-011 TYPE 'E'.
*
*  ENDIF.

*  For other Criteria, all fields except Search Term are needed
*  IF s_patnr  IS INITIAL AND
*   ( p_role   IS INITIAL OR
*     s_eccorg[] IS INITIAL OR
*     p_custcl IS INITIAL OR
*     p_indust IS INITIAL ).
*
*    MESSAGE text-014 TYPE 'E'.
*
*  ENDIF.


ENDFORM.                    " ZF_SCREEN_VALIDATIONS


